{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/dev/coq-setup/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"obtuseCave","author":"Han, Minhee","siteUrl":"https://han-minhee.github.io/blog","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"han-minhee/blog"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"esTfNE7"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c313ca34-df7e-5fed-ba43-997a8f857c66","excerpt":"Get the script Add the coq repo Install dependency Init Opam To install opam in Crostini or WSL, you need to disable sandboxing, so we add the flag to disable bwrap sandboxing. Input desired ocaml compiler version. Install Coq Install desired coq version. Install CoqIDE","html":"<h3 id=\"get-the-script\"><a href=\"#get-the-script\" aria-label=\"get the script permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Get the script</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sh</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ocaml/opam/master/shell/install.sh<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"add-the-coq-repo\"><a href=\"#add-the-coq-repo\" aria-label=\"add the coq repo permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Add the coq repo</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">opam repo <span class=\"token function\">add</span> coq-released https://coq.inria.fr/opam/released</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"install-dependency\"><a href=\"#install-dependency\" aria-label=\"install dependency permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install dependency</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token function\">git</span> build-essential patch <span class=\"token function\">unzip</span> m4</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"init-opam\"><a href=\"#init-opam\" aria-label=\"init opam permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Init Opam</h3>\n<p>To install opam in Crostini or WSL, you need to disable sandboxing, so we add the flag to disable bwrap sandboxing. Input desired ocaml compiler version.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">opam init -n --compiler<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>ocaml-base-compiler.4.07.1 --disable-sandboxing</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"install-coq\"><a href=\"#install-coq\" aria-label=\"install coq permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install Coq</h3>\n<p>Install desired coq version.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">opam <span class=\"token function\">install</span> coq.8.9.0</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"install-coqide\"><a href=\"#install-coqide\" aria-label=\"install coqide permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install CoqIDE</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> libgtksourceview2.0-dev\nopam <span class=\"token function\">install</span> coqide.8.9.0</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Install and setup opam/coq in debian / ubuntu","date":"July 13, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/dev/coq-setup/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/essay/2019-07-08-unrequited_love/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Sorrows and Rejoicings of Unrequited Love","category":"essays"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/dev/wsl-debian-setting/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Setup Debian WSL on Windows","category":"devs"}}}}}